      "body": "tACK [f899674](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/34919/commits/f89967463933c5e1c7dd3e841813035c1ff260dc)\r\n\r\nI was able to test that \r\n\r\n1. We were not covering this test on master 2fe76ed8324af44c985b96455a05c3e8bec0a03e\r\n2. The test suite failed with patch applied on [f899674](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/34919/commits/f89967463933c5e1c7dd3e841813035c1ff260dc)\r\n3. The test suite passed without the patch applied on [f899674](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/34919/commits/f89967463933c5e1c7dd3e841813035c1ff260dc)",
